Of course, at its front, there would be the front hair.

135
00:06:22,371 --> 00:06:24,582
And this would be the back hair.

136
00:06:25,105 --> 00:06:28,240
So, you can largely divide

137
00:06:28,242 --> 00:06:29,980
the hair into three parts.

138
00:06:30,005 --> 00:06:33,054
