00:26:23,536 --> 00:26:25,269
This part is curved forwards.

547
00:26:25,294 --> 00:26:27,661
Add some irregularity to it.

548
00:26:28,272 --> 00:26:29,435
The direction changes here.

549
00:26:30,419 --> 00:26:33,643
Decide whether or not you want to add irregularity.

550
00:26:34,425 --> 00:26:35,786
It's not really necessary.

551
00:26:36,185 --> 00:26:39,630
But, if you repeat adding it in and not adding it in,

552
00:26:40,302 --> 00:26:43,224
the hair will look quite natural.

553
00:26:43,499 --> 00:26:46,418
You could draw a curled up hair like this,

554
00:26:46,495 --> 00:26:48,186
or you can draw a waved hair or a permed hair.

555
00:26:48,187 --> 00:26:50,582
I'll show you an example of a slightly permed hair.

