00:27:28,192 --> 00:27:30,591
You'll understand it better this way.

571
00:27:33,622 --> 00:27:35,006
When you're drawing waved or permed hair,

572
00:27:35,008 --> 00:27:36,907
you should make sure that the hair has volume.

573
00:27:36,908 --> 00:27:38,773
It is really important to

