1250
01:03:37,083 --> 01:03:40,768
the cloth will have little to no thickness.

1251
01:03:41,065 --> 01:03:42,738
This area would just be a dot.

1252
01:03:42,740 --> 01:03:45,173
So, to create thickness,

1253
01:03:45,174 --> 01:03:47,494
would be to disconnect these lines.

1254
01:03:48,463 --> 01:03:50,380
