1257
01:03:55,692 --> 01:03:57,190
But, what would happen here?

1258
01:03:57,346 --> 01:04:03,111
There's the upper dimension, the inner dimension,

1259
01:04:04,354 --> 01:04:05,522
and the third dimension,

1260
01:04:06,377 --> 01:04:08,096
which is the lower dimension.

1261
01:04:09,799 --> 01:04:11,016
This is very important.

1262
01:04:11,041 --> 01:04:12,584
Whether this dimension exists or not

1263
01:04:12,608 --> 01:04:14,401
